
Targets to achieve for this app:

    - mark yourself safe
    - report safe place if its found (either set a threshold or may be govt can approve that place)
    - share images and coordinates of safe place
    - search your family by setting up your hotspot as your phone number
    - create a portal which shows all the safe location so as people or govt can help the public who are stuck there.
    - mark your location if u are not safe, the rescuer team will go there.
